trans-unit.source: Specifies the resource consumed by the member of a class.
trans-unit.target: Especifica el recurso utilizado por el miembro de una clase.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase no puede heredarse.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute> attribute is applied to a member, the <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceExposureAttribute> attribute must also be applied.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute> atributo se aplica a un miembro, el <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceExposureAttribute> atributo también deben aplicarse.

trans-unit.source: If the resource scope of the consumed resource is different than the resource scope of how it is consumed, the constructor that takes a `consumptionScope` parameter should be used to specify how the resource is consumed.
trans-unit.target: Si el ámbito de recurso del recurso utilizado es diferente que el ámbito de recursos de modo se consume, el constructor que toma un `consumptionScope` parámetro debe usarse para especificar cómo se consume el recurso.

trans-unit.source: For example, a resource may be exposed as a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> resource, but only used at the <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> and <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Assembly> scope.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, un recurso se puede exponer como un <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> recursos, pero solo se usa en la <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> y <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Assembly> ámbito.

trans-unit.source: For this example the `consumptionScope` parameter is set to <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> | <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Assembly>.
trans-unit.target: En este ejemplo el `consumptionScope` parámetro está establecido en <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> | <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Assembly>.

trans-unit.source: The `resourceScope` parameter in the constructor must specify a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope> greater than or equal to the resource exposure of all called members.
trans-unit.target: El `resourceScope` parámetro en el constructor debe especificar un <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope> mayor o igual que la exposición de recursos de todos los miembros llamados.

trans-unit.source: For example, a method consuming two <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> resources and one <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> resource would be identified as consuming a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> and a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> resource by setting `resourceScope` to <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> | <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process>.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, un método consumiendo dos <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> recursos y otro <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> recurso sería identificado como el de un <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> y un <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> recursos estableciendo `resourceScope` a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> | <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process>.

trans-unit.source: `Public` members cannot expose <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Assembly> or <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Private> resources.
trans-unit.target: `Public` no se pueden exponer los miembros <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Assembly> o <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Private> recursos.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Assembly> members cannot expose <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Private> resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Assembly> no se pueden exponer los miembros <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Private> recursos.

trans-unit.source: The graph of methods terminates when a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceExposureAttribute> attribute with a resource scope of <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.None> is applied to a method.
trans-unit.target: El gráfico de métodos finaliza cuando un <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceExposureAttribute> atributo con un ámbito de recurso de <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.None> se aplica a un método.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> for the consumed resource.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> para el recurso utilizado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute" /> class specifying the scope of the consumed resource.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute" /> que especifica el ámbito del recurso utilizado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> for the consumed resource.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> para el recurso utilizado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> used by this member.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> que utiliza este miembro.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute" /> class specifying the scope of the consumed resource and the scope of how it is consumed.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute" /> que especifica el ámbito del recurso utilizado y el ámbito del modo de utilización.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceExposureAttribute> attribute specifies a scope of <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.None>, then the <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute> attribute must specify a resource it consumes and how it consumes it, by specifying a value for the `consumptionScope` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceExposureAttribute> atributo especifica un ámbito de <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.None>, la <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceConsumptionAttribute> atributo debe especificar un recurso que utiliza y cómo lo utiliza, especificando un valor para el `consumptionScope` parámetro.

trans-unit.source: The scope specified by `consumptionScope` should be less than or equal to the scope specified by `resourceScope`.
trans-unit.target: El ámbito especificado por `consumptionScope` debe ser menor o igual que el ámbito especificado por `resourceScope`.

trans-unit.source: For example, a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> scope can be consumed as a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> or <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.AppDomain> scope, but not as a <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> scope.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, un <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> ámbito puede utilizarse como un <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Process> o <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.AppDomain> ámbito, pero no como un <xref:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope.Machine> ámbito.

trans-unit.source: Gets the consumption scope for this member.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el ámbito de utilización de este miembro.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> object specifying the resource scope used by this member.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> que especifica el ámbito de recurso utilizado por este miembro.

trans-unit.source: Gets the resource scope for the consumed resource.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el ámbito de recurso para el recurso utilizado.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> object specifying the resource scope of the consumed member.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Versioning.ResourceScope" /> que especifica el ámbito de recurso del miembro utilizado.
